author: juergen
msg: Changed status for DeltaV precondition violation <DAV:cannot-modify-protected-property> from Forbidden to Conflict. Due to precondtion semantics it should be a Forbidden, but since PropPatchMethod already sends a Conflict when trying to patch non-DeltaV protected properties this might be more consistent.
